<div class="row" >
  <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12 " style= "text-align:left" >

All items offered for sale through CrowdPublish.TV are meant to be immediately available and fulfilled within a week. So if you're offering to tweet to them, do it as soon as you see their contribution posted on your dashboard. If you're offering an hour of consulting time, text or call to arrange a session right away! Check your dashboard often.<br><br>

          <% if !current_user.stripeid.present? %>
            You must Sign Up for Stripe to receive payments 
              <a href="https://connect.stripe.com/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=<%= STRIPECONNECTCLIENTID %>&scope=read_write" target="_blank"><%= link_to image_tag("stripebutton.png") %></a>
          <% end %><br><br>

<h3>Offer a new Patron Perk</h3>

<%= form_for(@merchandise) do |f| %>
  <% if @merchandise.errors.any? %>
    <div id="error_explanation">
      <h2><%= pluralize(@merchandise.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this merchandise from being saved:</h2>
      <ul> <% @merchandise.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
        <li><%= msg %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="blacktxt">
    <b>Patron Perk name </b><br>
    <%= f.text_field :name, size: 80, placeholder: "The Best Stuff Ever" %><br><br>
    <b>Perk Picture </b><br>
        Upload a picture that represents the item you are offering (.jpg, .gif, .jpeg, or .png) - <i>a square picture works best</i>
        <br><%= f.file_field :itempic %> 
    <b>About this perk </b> - You may add to this later<br>
    <%= f.text_area :desc, cols: 82, :rows => 7, placeholder: "What is this product? What is the main reason someone might want this item?" %><br><br>
    <b>Price </b><br>
      $<%= f.text_field :price, size: 70, value: 50.00 || :price %>USD<br>
  </div>

  <div class="blacktxt">
    <b>Video </b><br>
      If you have a video about your item on <b>YouTube</b>, paste the YouTube URL below. Your video's 11-digit ID will be saved. Any non-YouTube url will be ignored. <br /> 
      <div class="profilebox" >
        <%= f.text_area :youtube, cols: 70, rows: 2, placeholder: 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=/frlviTJcVUo' %>
      </div><br>
  </div>

    <b>Get It While It's Hot! </b><br>
    What day do fans have to purchase this Perk before?<br>
    <%= f.date_select :expiration, selected: Date.today + 2.months, :start_year => Date.today.year, :end_year => Date.today.year + 1 %>

  <div class="actions">
    <%= f.submit "Add Perk" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
<br><br>

<% if !current_user.stripeid.present? %>
  You must 
        <% if Rails.env.development? || Rails.env.test? %>
          <a href="https://connect.stripe.com/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=<%= STRIPE_CONNECT_CLIENT_ID %>&scope=read_write" target="_blank">Sign up for Stripe </a>
        <% else %>
          <a href="https://connect.stripe.com/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=<%= ENV['STRIPE_CONNECT_CLIENT_ID'] %>&scope=read_write" target="_blank">Sign up for Stripe </a>
        <% end %>
  before offering items for sale.
<% end %>
</div>
</div>
